data.description: Welcome home! The fantastic floor plan ensures a comfortable living experience, with ample space and natural light throughout. The spacious living room is adorned with a cozy gas fireplace and recently upgraded flooring. The well-appointed kitchen features granite countertops, an electric cooktop, a recently replaced dishwasher, and is also plumbed for gas. The kitchen overlooks both the dining area and the living room, creating a harmonious flow for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. The backyard features an extended concrete patio with boundless potential. This space invites you to envision and create your dream outdoor living area. Paloma Creek has so much to offer and is conveniently located near major highways, shopping, and tons of dining options. Community features include amenities centers, pools, trails, fitness centers, and parks. Schedule a showing today and make this house your home.
